Package org.aludratest.data.configtests

Class Summary
AbstractConfigTest Abstract parent test class for testing the default Excel test data parser.
ConfigTestWithAddidtionalConfigRow Tests the default Excel test data parser with a test case that uses an Excel sheet with an additional config row (respectively a missing data row).
ConfigTestWithHierarchy  
ConfigTestWithIgnoreConfig Tests the TestConfigInfoHelper with a test case that uses an Excel sheet with a properly formatted 'config' tab and 'testConfiguration' column.
ConfigTestWithIgnoredMethod Tests the default Excel test data parser with a test case that uses an Excel sheet with a properly formatted 'config' tab and 'testConfiguration' column and a method that has been annotated as Ignored.
ConfigTestWithMissingConfigRow Tests the TestConfigInfoHelper with a test case that uses an Excel sheet with a missing config row.
ConfigTestWithMissingSource Tests the TestConfigInfoHelper with a test case that refers a missing Excel file.
ConfigTestWithMissingTab Tests the default Excel test data parser with a test case that uses an Excel sheet without 'config' tab.
ConfigTestWithProperConfig Tests the TestConfigInfoHelper with a test case that uses an Excel sheet with a properly formatted 'config' tab and 'testConfiguration' column.
